# --- Tenant isolation (CLIENT/ETEC BRANCH OVERRIDE) ---
# This branch (client/etec) intentionally diverges from main here.
# Master plan §9 requires _inbox/, intake/, workspace/ to be trackable on
# the client branch. The three patterns that catch them are present on main
# but removed here. Tenant isolation guarantees on this branch rest on:
#   1. Branch policy (master plan §3.4) — client/* never merges to main.
#   2. PreToolUse hook (.claude/hooks/tenant-boundary-check.py) — blocks
#      Edit/Write/MultiEdit on core paths (knowledge/, scripts/,
#      DGA-Resources/, extracted/) from client/* branches.
# DO NOT MERGE THIS .gitignore TO MAIN. The patterns must remain on main.
